HEADWORD: midsummer-men
<hw>midsummer-men</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A Eurasian
mountain plant (<spn>Sedum rosea</spn>) with fleshy pink-tipped leaves
and a cluster of yellow flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> rose-root, <spn>Sedum rosea</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
